<h3>Travel to Madrid, Spain</h3>

<div style="overflow:auto;">
    <p>
        The <a href="http://avenidaamerica.madridhotels.it/" target="_blank">Hotel Melia Avenida de America</a> provides free shuttle bus service from <a href="http://www.aena-aeropuertos.es/csee/Satellite/Aeropuerto-Madrid-Barajas/en/" target="_blank">Barajas airport</a> <!--(more detailed information will follow)-->.
        
        If you are not going straight to the hotel, the Metro (pink; line nº 8 ) is the easiest and cheapest way to and from the airport (4,5 €).
    </p>

    <p> 
        <p>The hotel offers a shuttle service to and from the airport, available from 7 am - 11 pm (continued service).</p>
 
        <p><b>Hotel Melia Avenida America</b><br/>
        Calle de Juan Ignacio Luca de Tena, 36 Madrid, ESPAÑA<br/>
        Telephone: +34 91 4232400</p>
 
        <p>Stops are located at:<br/>
        <ul>
            <li>Terminal 1, room 2</li>
            <li>Terminal 2, room 5</li>
            <li>Terminal 4, dock 1</li>
        </ul>
        </p>

        <p>To avoid waiting, we recommend you call the hotel (91 4232400 - when in Spain) and ask for the service upon arrival, so if the bus is in another terminal they will still pick you up.</p>
    </p>

    <h4>From the hotel to the city center (see map 1)</h4>
    <p>
        There is a taxi stop just outside the hotel front door, on the left.
    </p> 
    <p>
        Three city buses are running close to the hotel (approximately from 6:30 – 23:30)
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>146 goes to the city center</li> 
        <li>114 goes to the airport cargo area</li>
        <li>104 goes north to Mar de Cristal</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        There is also a Metro stop (Suanzes) on the green Metro line nº 5 located a 10-15 min. walk from the hotel (see map 1) or the full <a href="http://www.madbudget.com/madrid-metro-map" target="_blank"/>Metro map</a>
    </p>

    <p>General Madrid public transport information is <a href="http://www.ctm-madrid.es/" target="_blank">available</a>.</p>

