    <h4>Important remarks</h4>
    <p>
        It is very easy to find information online about Madrid. If there is any particular thing you cannot find, please, ask us.
    </p>
    <p>
        <b>Around the hotel</b>: The hotel is located in a business area of Madrid and therefore not especially attractive. However there is a very nice garden <a href="http://www.madripedia.es/wiki/Parque_Quinta_de_los_Molinos" target="_blank">Parque Quinta de los Molinos</a> at 5 minutes (see map 1), where you may take a relaxing walk.
    </p>

    <p><b>Weather</b>: it is hot and the sun is strong. Temperatures may easily reach 40º C (104º F) during the day, though up to now it has been a mild summer. You may need sun protection.
    </p>

    <p><b>Thefts</b>: be careful with your belongings, thefts are more common in touristic locations such as the airport.</p>

